R11AUD.original: ~z~Yes, the guy in Europe... who lives by the Adriatic.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~对，欧洲的那个...住亚得里亚海边上的。

R11AUD.original: ~z~You add these insults to the injuries I have already suffered.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你这些侮辱是在往我伤口上撒盐。

R11AUD.original: ~z~You are still new here, cousin. You do not understand.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你还是不熟悉这里，堂弟。你不明白。

R11AUD.original: ~z~I got here and I had nothing, nobody. I worked my way up from the fucking dirt.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我来的时候啥都没有，谁都不认识。~n~全他妈是从无到有奋斗出来的。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Do diamonds burn, cousin? How about gold, will that melt in a fire?
R11AUD.translated: ~z~钻石会烧着吗，堂弟？黄金呢，会不会在火里熔了？

R11AUD.original: ~z~I know a bunch of people who might be able to help out.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我认识挺多人的，说不定能帮上你。

R11AUD.original: ~z~I told you, you still have Mallorie.
~z~I've got nothing left. Not my home, not my business, nothing.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我什么都没剩下了。要家没家，要事业没事业，屁都不剩。

R11AUD.original: ~z~No, we are not. I was going to propose to her but it is no longer possible.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~不是，还没呢。我本来是要跟她求婚了，但现在不可能了。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Now, I have nothing to spend... nothing. Oh yeah, I have you. Great.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~现在我都没东西可以挥霍了...没了。噢，对，我还有你。真好。

R11AUD.original: ~z~This was the engagement ring I bought for Mallorie.
~z~Oh yeah, thanks Niko! Thanks a bunch! Is that better?
R11AUD.translated: ~z~哦耶，谢了Niko！多谢啊！这样就好了？

R11AUD.original: ~z~Great, see you in a bit, beautiful.
~z~Then we shut everything up and get to Bohan.
~z~I do not have a ring. It burnt in my apartment along with everything else.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我没了戒指。在我的公寓里跟其他东西一起烧掉了。

R11AUD.original: ~z~You got off the boat and I was here for you.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你一下船我就在那儿等好了。

R11AUD.original: ~z~I've got to go to work. Bye, Pappy.
~z~I am sorry that your worldly possessions have been destroyed, but you were not that rich a man.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~很抱歉你那些世俗财产都被毁了，但是你又没那么富。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Dimitri was not a man of his word.
~z~Is simple, we go collect our stuff from the apartment and the depot.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~很简单，我们先去公寓和车行收拾下行李。

R11AUD.original: ~z~My dream, it was just that... a dream.
~z~my apartment got burned down and so did my business.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~公寓给人烧了，车行也给烧了。

R11AUD.original: ~z~You have a lot to apologize for. Since you got here I've had my computer smashed,
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你要道歉的事可多了去了。~n~自打你来了以后，我电脑给人砸了，

R11AUD.original: ~z~Please... come on, let's go back to the apartment.
~z~Listen, me and Niko are in a bit of trouble - need to get out of Broker a few days.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~听我说，我和Niko遇上了点小麻烦，要离开Broker避几天风头。

R11AUD.original: ~z~We will, but I have left something important at the apartment. Something I must show you, cousin.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~肯定会，不过我在公寓里落了样重要的东西。你一定要看看那个，堂弟。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Do you know how long it took me to get a place of my own?
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你知道我花了多久才有了自己的家吗？

R11AUD.original: ~z~It was just a joke... about the whores, you know?
R11AUD.translated: ~z~刚才是个玩笑...关于妓女的，你知道吗？

R11AUD.original: ~z~I've been beaten up, I was kidnapped and then shot in the stomach,
R11AUD.translated: ~z~自己给人打了，还给人绑走了，往肚子上来了一枪，

R11AUD.original: ~z~cars and the sharp clothes and my beautiful Mallorie.
~z~Maybe they will let us live with them in their crack dens.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~说不定就让我们跟她们一起住烟馆里了。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Bulgarin and Dimitri shall not be happy that I survived our meeting.
~z~I'll call Mallorie, she might have somewhere we can hide out.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我给Mallorie打个电话，她可能有地方能让我们躲。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Do you know how long it took me to get set up here? You don't because it was easy for you.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你知道我为了在这里开店花了多久吗？~n~你不知道，因为你过得太容易了。

R11AUD.original: ~z~All I know is we have to get as far from Dimitri and Bulgarin as we can.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我只知道，我们离Dimitri和Bulgarin越远越好。

R11AUD.original: ~z~You remember that time we went to the bar back home and found it razed to the ground?
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你还记得当年我们去老家的酒吧，结果发现店被夷为平地吗？

R11AUD.original: ~z~They burnt it... they fucking burnt it, Niko!
R11AUD.translated: ~z~他们居然放火...他们居然他妈放火，Niko！

R11AUD.original: ~z~What are we going to do in Bohan? Pick up the whores on Chase Point?
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我们去Bohan干嘛？去Chase Point勾搭妓女吗？

R11AUD.original: ~z~We can pick up our stuff, and then get out of here.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我们可以去收拾下行李，然后就离开这儿。

R11AUD.original: ~z~You had it all from day one. It took me months to get some cash together.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你来的第一天就啥都有了。~n~我花了好几个月才凑出一点钱。

R11AUD.original: ~z~except for that one bottle of vodka.
~z~Holy fuck, it's fucking burning. The whole place... I've got to go in, I've got to get something.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~操他妈的，他妈着火了。整栋楼...我要进去，我要进去拿东西。

R11AUD.original: ~z~At least they want me dead and not you.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~至少他们要的是我的命，不是你的。

R11AUD.original: ~z~You know what you can catch from those girls?
~z~Things have been going so great, just great, since you showed up.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~自打你来了以后，发生的事情都很好，真的好。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Now, you know everything is shit and we are going to be killed, and you're all cheerful.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~现在你知道什么都完了，我们要死了，反而还很开心。

R11AUD.original: ~z~I got scared... people started calling the house and hanging up.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我吓坏了...家里的座机响个不停。

R11AUD.original: ~z~-bunch of idiot Russians... ~n~-I will kill every one of them.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~－不就是群俄罗斯傻蛋吗...~n~－我会把他们一一杀掉。

R11AUD.original: ~z~We can lay low... and start over.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我们可以低调做人...从头开始。

R11AUD.original: ~z~I'm glad you turned up and made some Russian killers burn down my home and business!
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你来了搞的一群俄国杀手烧了我的家和车行我可真高兴。

R11AUD.original: ~z~You have your life, Roman. You have a life which is worth a lot more than mine at the moment.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你有你的生活，Roman。现在你的生活比我的更有价值。

R11AUD.original: ~z~I do not care though. We are in this situation. We must deal with it.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~不过我不在乎。我们都这样了，就必须面对它。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Even I would not go with those hookers on the point, cousin.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~就连我都不会去那里叫鸡，堂弟。

R11AUD.original: ~z~I don't want to talk about back home.
~z~I was thinking about getting out of the cab business. Last night I had a dream...
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我刚好有想过不做的士生意。昨晚我做了个梦...

R11AUD.original: ~z~I am glad you have a sense of humor about this now.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~很高兴你现在还能有这种幽默感。

R11AUD.original: ~z~This could be the start of that. A fresh beginning.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~这就可以是梦的开始。全新的起点。

R11AUD.original: ~z~No. Don't be like that... we can find a way out of this...
~z~I always put a saddle on a horse before I ride her, Roman. I won't catch nothing.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我上马之前总会先套个鞍的，Roman。不会得脏病的。

R11AUD.original: ~z~You're an angel - beautiful and kind. I love you. We'll see you there.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你真是天使，美丽而善良。我爱你。我们那边见。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Any of your cousins have a place we could use out in Bohan?
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你有没有哪个亲戚在Bohan有地方给我们住的？

R11AUD.original: ~z~Just a pile of rubble... everything smashed,
~z~You weren't answering your phone! What happened?
~z~One dead Bellic will give them a little bit of happiness while they wait for next.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~死一个Bellic他们就开心一点，就想杀下一个。

R11AUD.original: ~z~We don't have time for revenge. We can't afford it.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我们没时间复仇了，负担不起的。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Well, it doesn't matter. Now it's gone along with everything else.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~现在都无所谓了，全都化为灰烬了。

R11AUD.original: ~z~I mean, I don't think we'll be impressing women with our wonderful hot tub, but, err, this looks okay...
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我是说，虽然我不觉得这个豪华开放浴缸会给女士们留下好印象，不过...看起来还挺好。

R11AUD.original: ~z~You are a sick fuck, cousin. No wonder half of Broker wants you dead.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你这人哪，堂弟。难怪半个Broker的人都想要你的命。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Yeah... we sat down and finished it off there and then. Wait... wait...
R11AUD.translated: ~z~记得...我们坐下来，在那儿把酒喝完了。~n~打住...打住...

R11AUD.original: ~z~You know what? I think maybe they might get me when going after you.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你知道吗？我觉得他们追杀你的时候可能会来抓我。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Fine and now this. Thank you. Thanks a lot!
R11AUD.translated: ~z~结果现在呢。谢谢你啊，真是多谢啊！

R11AUD.original: ~z~A classy place. None of this fast-food, diner bullshit. We own a real restaurant, a tavern.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~精致的地儿，不是什么垃圾快餐小饭店。我们开的是真正的餐厅，一家酒馆。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Must think about the future. A new apartment in South Bohan, another business,
R11AUD.translated: ~z~该好好想想未来了。在South Bohan的新公寓，新的事业。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Pure like my Mallorie. In the dream Mallorie and me are married.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~和我的Mallorie一样纯洁。在梦里我和Mallorie结婚了。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Sure it was, Niko. Sure it was.
~z~Yes, you and I had a place of our own. A place where people come to eat and relax.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~对，你和我有了自己的一亩三分地。别人来这儿吃饭休闲。

R11AUD.original: ~z~That seems like the pattern of events since you get here.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你来了以后好像都是这么回事。

R11AUD.original: ~z~In here. I'm stuck. Let me out...
~z~Here we are, the beginning of our new lives... again.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~就是这儿了，我们新生活的开始...重新开始。

R11AUD.original: ~z~You cannot escape the past. Only thing is future, right?
R11AUD.translated: ~z~人无法逃避过去。眼前只会有未来，对吧？

R11AUD.original: ~z~No... that's exactly what you won't do.
~z~I do not speak of diamonds, but of one diamond and a band of gold.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我说的不是很多钻石，只有一颗钻石和一个金环。

R11AUD.original: ~z~We're here in America now and I should be thinking about my life here, my life which is ruined.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我们现在在美国，我想的应该是这里的生活，已经被毁掉的生活。

R11AUD.original: ~z~I am the one end up feeling the pain after you piss people off.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~每次你把人惹恼了，最后都是我挨打。

R11AUD.original: ~z~That guy I owed money to, Bulgarin.

R11AUD.translated: ~z~我是不觉得自己能安定下来。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Only thing I see in my future is more people trying to kill me.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我在未来里只看见了更多想杀我的人。

R11AUD.original: ~z~It was worthy of her. Now I have nothing!
~z~I'm sorry, Roman. I tell you, I am sorry.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我很抱歉，Roman。我跟你讲，我很抱歉。

R11AUD.original: ~z~And you, for all the good you've done me.
~z~I do not spend money at these games, I risk it for reward.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~赌博不是为了挥霍，我是去搏一搏的。

R11AUD.original: ~z~It is a place of distinction, you know?
~z~That is what I wanted to show you. It was a beautiful ring.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~就是刚才想给你看的那个，真的很好看的戒指。

R11AUD.original: ~z~I guess you cannot escape your past.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我想你也逃避不了你的过去。

R11AUD.original: ~z~I'm sorry, Roman, I'm really sorry but we have to go.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我很抱歉，Roman，真的很抱歉，但我们得走了。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Where should I start? Alright, I'll start with you - what's wrong with you?
R11AUD.translated: ~z~你让我从哪开始说？算了，从你说起吧。你有毛病吗？
~z~没事的，我就是从这里出来的，Niko。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Anyway, you will not have to become some crack whore's pimp.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~反正呢，你是不会去当什么拉皮条的的。

R11AUD.original: ~z~I risk my bets to win more so I can spend on the hot
R11AUD.translated: ~z~压上我的筹码，赢走更多筹码，这样我就可以把钱花在

R11AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, trying to impress Michelle or something.
~z~a bigger diamond for Mallorie. The future, yes?
R11AUD.translated: ~z~给Mallorie买个更大的钻石。未来，对吧？

R11AUD.original: ~z~I get Mallorie to arrange place for us to stay in South Bohan.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我让Mallorie给我们在South Bohan安置了一下。

R11AUD.original: ~z~I do not think it will be much difference to them, Niko.
~z~Fifteen minutes ago you were cowering in fear because you didn't know what was going to happen.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~一刻钟之前，你还因为不知道会发生什么吓得瑟瑟发抖。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Finally I bought a cab and then another, then I got the depot...
R11AUD.translated: ~z~终于我买下了第一辆的士，~n~然后是第二辆，然后开起了车行...

R11AUD.original: ~z~But I wanted to really have her. I wanted to marry her.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~但是我想真正拥有她。我想和她结婚。

R11AUD.original: ~z~We're fucked - we're broke and on the run.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我们被人搞了，现在是破产在逃。

R11AUD.original: ~z~America is about showing what you have, you express yourself with money you spend.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~在美国就是要展现财富，要靠挥霍金钱来表现自己。

R11AUD.original: ~z~You probably would have gambled them away if there had been anyway.
~z~There were not diamonds and gold in that apartment.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~那公寓里哪来的钻石跟黄金。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Why don't you come and meet me at the community center later on?
R11AUD.translated: ~z~要么你待会儿来社区中心找我？

R11AUD.original: ~z~We're coming to your cousin's, are you there?
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我们要来你亲戚的地儿了，你在吗？

R11AUD.original: ~z~Not now, but in the dream you've met the right woman. She is beautiful.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~现在是不能，但是在梦里你遇到了那个她。她很美。

R11AUD.original: ~z~What are you expressing when you spend your money in backroom card games?
R11AUD.translated: ~z~那你在地下赌场挥霍的时候是想表现什么？

R11AUD.original: ~z~And, perhaps, a date with the man I came to this city to find.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~然后，也许是和我来这里寻找的人见上一面。

R11AUD.original: ~z~I slept under my desk at that place for over a year...
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我在车行的桌子底下睡了一年多...

R11AUD.original: ~z~I will add that to the long list of your secrets that are safe with me.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我会把它加进你的秘密清单里的，不会泄露的。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Come on, Roman, pull yourself together. You've been here before.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~振作点，Roman，鼓起劲来。也不是没这样过。

R11AUD.original: ~z~We'll meet Mallorie in Bohan. You still have her.
~z~I haven't been crying, it's my allergies. Niko's wearing this new cologne.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我没在哭，只是过敏了。Niko喷了点新香水。

R11AUD.original: ~z~Roman, you sound like you did in those emails you sent me before I arrived here.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~Roman，你发给我的邮件里面不都是梦话吗。

R11AUD.original: ~z~then I got the apartment, the apartment you thought was so shitty.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~之后我买下了公寓，你还嫌弃它烂的公寓。

R11AUD.original: ~z~You do not need a ring to propose. Mallorie loves you for who you are, not for some ring.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~求婚不需要戒指。Mallorie爱的不是什么戒指，是你。

R11AUD.original: ~z~And have a shower - you smell a little, erm, mature?
R11AUD.translated: ~z~记得去洗个澡。你身上有点，呃，男人味？

R11AUD.original: ~z~I can't have the tavern now. I have nothing to buy it with. I have, I have nothing.
R11AUD.translated: ~z~我现在开不了酒馆了，根本就买不起。~n~现在我、我啥都没有了。
